Description_lang: Allows a cook to create steamed delicacies, up to a maximum skill of 75.

description_blz.en_US: Allows a cook to create steamed delicacies, up to a maximum skill of 75.

description_blz.pt_BR: Permite ao cozinheiro preparar delícias cozidas a vapor até o nível 75.
description_blz.de_DE: Ermöglicht einem Koch, gedämpfte Delikatessen mit einer maximalen Fertigkeit von 75 zu kochen.
